subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Sixth-seeded Purdue, which had lost to North Carolina in two of the past three N.C.A.A. tournaments, defeated the third-seeded Tar Heals, 85-70, in the second round.
